msgid "Timer"
msgstr "计时器"

#: ../../source/functions/utilities/timer.md:3
msgid ""
"A countdown timer that can perform a sequence of actions when the timer "
"starts or ends. You can configure alarms for when the timer finishes."
msgstr ""
"倒计时计时器，可以在计时器开始或结束时执行一系列操作。您可以为计时器结束时配置警报。"

