msgid "Set the countdown duration"
msgstr "设置倒计时持续时间"

#: ../../source/functions/utilities/timer.md:10
msgid ""
"Choose the alarm type when countdown ends: disabled, button alarm, or "
"full-screen alarm"
msgstr ""
"选择倒计时结束时的警报类型：禁用、按钮警报或全屏警报"

#: ../../source/functions/utilities/timer.md:11
msgid "Option to hide the countdown time display"
msgstr "隐藏倒计时时间显示的选项"

#: ../../source/functions/utilities/timer.md:12
msgid "Position of the countdown time display"
msgstr "倒计时时间显示的位置"

#: ../../source/functions/utilities/timer.md:13
msgid ""
"Actions to execute when the countdown starts/ends, configured the same "
"way as [Sequenced Keys](../more/sequenced_keys.md)"
msgstr ""
"倒计时开始/结束时执行的操作，配置方式与 [序列按键](../more/sequenced_keys.md) 相同"

#: ../../source/functions/utilities/timer.md:15
msgid "On the Flexbar"
msgstr "在 Flexbar 上"

#: ../../source/functions/utilities/timer.md:17
msgid ""
"When the countdown starts, a semi-transparent black overlay shows the "
"progress. An alarm will sound when the countdown ends."
msgstr ""
"倒计时开始时，半透明黑色覆盖层显示进度。倒计时结束时将发出警报声。"

